<p>
New in version 0.8:

<ul>
	<li>Upon revoking access for a user to the vpn, the certificates will now be added to the certificate revocation list</li>
	<li>The ready2go-packages will automatically be regenerated upon config changes to the server-side</li>
	<li>The ready2go-packages now contain a configuration file for use with Windows clients as well</li>
	<li>Highly improved tooltips, naming and descriptions</li>
	<li>Removed some config options and replaced them with sane defaults</li>
</ul>
</p>

